news.title: Levi Strauss to sell Dockers to brand management firm Authentic Brands Group
news.summary: Levi's announced plans to sell Dockers to Authentic Brands Group. The brand management firm owns the IP for Forever 21, Reebok and other brands.

news.title: D-Wave Quantum shares soar 20% as company releases latest computing system
news.summary: D-Wave Quantum's latest quantum computing system has hit the market, the company said Tuesday. D-Wave says it's the world's first quantum computing device.

news.title: Trump allows New York offshore wind project after apparent gas pipeline compromise with state
news.summary: Empire Wind 1 would have been the first offshore wind project to deliver electricity directly to New York City. The project was to have been built in the waters off Long Island.

news.title: New report shows the staggering AI cash surge — and the rise of the 'zombiecorn'
news.summary: About 40% of the money raised by U.S. startups last year came from funds focused on AI. A new report from Silicon Valley Bank shows that.

news.title: Home Depot CFO says retailer doesn't plan to raise prices due to tariffs
news.summary: Home Depot reaffirmed its full-year guidance, even as it missed Wall Street's earnings estimates. Customers continued to put off bigger home projects.
